<p>The intent was to suggest that self-taught individuals may be more passionate about a subject, as it is that passion that drives them to learn. It may have been clearer to question who you would rather have making the cut, given the option (assuming that either would have the support of relevant experts).</p>
<p>Ideally, one would have both a broad skill set and strong devotion to the subject matter.<!-- Touched by JuLiA --></p>
				

